    <h2 style="color: #FF5733; font-weight: bold;">Welcome to the Movie Booking App!</h2>
    <p>Experience the ultimate movie booking platform where you can browse and book tickets for the latest blockbuster movies. Whether you are a fan of action, romance, comedy, or thriller, we have a diverse selection of movies that cater to all tastes.</p>
    <p style="color: #20CD8D">How it Works:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Browse Movies: Explore a wide range of movies currently showing in theaters. Get detailed information about each movie, including its genre, duration, release date, language, and user ratings.</li>
        <li>Book Tickets: Easily book movie tickets for your favorite shows and theaters. Choose your preferred showtime and seating options for a seamless booking experience.</li>
        <li>Special Offers: Keep an eye out for special offers, discounts, and exclusive deals on movie tickets and concessions to enhance your movie-going experience.</li>
        <li>Secure Payments: Enjoy secure and hassle-free online payments for your ticket bookings. We accept multiple payment methods to ensure convenience and safety.</li>
        <li>My Bookings: Access your booking history and manage your upcoming movie reservations. You can also cancel or modify your bookings based on availability.</li>
        <li>Rate and Review: Share your movie-watching experiences by rating and reviewing the movies you've watched. Your feedback will help other movie enthusiasts make informed decisions.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>With our user-friendly interface and seamless booking process, we aim to make your movie-watching experience enjoyable and stress-free. Start exploring the latest movies and book your tickets today!</p>
    <p>For any assistance or inquiries, feel free to contact our customer support team. Enjoy the show!</p>
